            <title>[LU-16957] Improve parallel --config-cache</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16957</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the parallel build does not consider the configure cache before re-testing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should be fixed and restore cache configure performance as well as ./configure ; make rpms with cache enabled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can also move more tests into a single parallel build step&lt;/p&gt;</description>
